title: mountain_guide
position: 250,0
color: blue
---
<<if $found_items == 7>>
    You are ready for the summit! #line:fr08_guide_ready
    <<jump question_summit_flags>>
<<elseif GetCurrentTask() == "find_gear">>
    Keep climbing! The air is getting colder. #line:fr08_guide_encourage
<<else>>
    Help! I am a mountain guide, but a blue dog took our climbing gear! #line:fr08_guide_1
    <<card backpack>>
    The gear is scattered at different bases up the mountain. #line:fr08_guide_2
    Can you find all 7 items so we can reach the top? #line:fr08_guide_3 #task:find_gear
    <<area area_all>>
    <<task_start find_gear task_gear_done>>
<<endif>>
===

