title: npc_base1_hiker
---
<<card coat>>
The wind is starting to blow. It is cold! #line:fr08_b1_1
<<if $step_base1 < 10>>
    How do we stay warm when the wind is strong? #line:fr08_b1_q
    -> Wear a thick coat #line:fr08_b1_a1
        <<set $step_base1 = 1>>
        <<target chest_base1>>
        Yes! Open the chest to get the gear. #line:fr08_b1_ok
    -> Wear a swimsuit #line:fr08_b1_a2
        No, you would freeze! Try again. #line:fr08_b1_no
        <<jump npc_base1_hiker>>
<<else>>
    You look much warmer now! #line:fr08_b1_done
<<endif>>
===

title: chest_base1
---
