title: npc_base3_glaciologist
---
<<card glacier>>
We are walking on a glacier! It is a river of ice. #line:fr08_b3_1
<<if $step_base3 < 10>>
    The sun is very bright on the white ice. What do you need? #line:fr08_b3_q
    -> Sunglasses and Crampons #line:fr08_b3_a1
        <<set $step_base3 = 1>>
        <<target chest_base3>>
        Yes! Sunglasses for your eyes and crampons for the ice. #line:fr08_b3_ok
    -> An umbrella #line:fr08_b3_a2
        That won't help you walk on ice! Try again. #line:fr08_b3_no
        <<jump npc_base3_glaciologist>>
<<else>>
    The view is beautiful, isn't it? #line:fr08_b3_done
<<endif>>
===

